<!DOCTYPE html>
<html><head><meta charset="UTF-8"><title>创建店铺</title></head>
<body>
  <div><a href="/shop">返回商城</a> | <a href="/friends">好友</a> | <a href="/chat">群聊</a> | <a href="/shop/create">开店</a></div>
  <hr>
  <h2>创建店铺</h2>
